output.sentences: "Say what!?" said Quincy. "You heard me." said Lurlene as her flashback manifested via telecommunications. Quincy, trying to maintain composure, but betrayed by his trembling voice, calmly panicked utters in disbelief. "But the door, I had Charles change the hinge last week. Now it's dual action. I can be made to open by Push. And. Pull." Cut to Black.
